=== Example 1: Different Table Styles ===
--- Single Style ---
┌───────────────┬─────┬─────────────┬──────────┐
│ Name          │ Age │ City        │ Status   │
├───────────────┼─────┼─────────────┼──────────┤
│ Alice Johnson │ 25  │ New York    │ Active   │
│ Bob Smith     │ 30  │ Los Angeles │ Inactive │
│ Charlie Brown │ 35  │ Chicago     │ Active   │
└───────────────┴─────┴─────────────┴──────────┘

--- Double Style ---
╔═══════════════╦═════╦═════════════╦══════════╗
║ Name          ║ Age ║ City        ║ Status   ║
╠═══════════════╬═════╬═════════════╬══════════╣
║ Alice Johnson ║ 25  ║ New York    ║ Active   ║
║ Bob Smith     ║ 30  ║ Los Angeles ║ Inactive ║
║ Charlie Brown ║ 35  ║ Chicago     ║ Active   ║
╚═══════════════╩═════╩═════════════╩══════════╝

--- Rounded Style ---
╭───────────────┬─────┬─────────────┬──────────╮
│ Name          │ Age │ City        │ Status   │
├───────────────┼─────┼─────────────┼──────────┤
│ Alice Johnson │ 25  │ New York    │ Active   │
│ Bob Smith     │ 30  │ Los Angeles │ Inactive │
│ Charlie Brown │ 35  │ Chicago     │ Active   │
╰───────────────┴─────┴─────────────┴──────────╯

--- ASCII Style ---
+---------------+-----+-------------+----------+
| Name          | Age | City        | Status   |
+---------------+-----+-------------+----------+
| Alice Johnson | 25  | New York    | Active   |
| Bob Smith     | 30  | Los Angeles | Inactive |
| Charlie Brown | 35  | Chicago     | Active   |
+---------------+-----+-------------+----------+

--- None Style ---

  Name            Age   City          Status

  Alice Johnson   25    New York      Active
  Bob Smith       30    Los Angeles   Inactive
  Charlie Brown   35    Chicago       Active


=== Example 2: Colored Table ===
╭──────────┬───────┬───────┬─────────────────╮
│ Product  │ Price │ Stock │ Status          │
├──────────┼───────┼───────┼─────────────────┤
│ Laptop   │ $999  │ 15    │ ✓ In Stock     │
│ Mouse    │ $25   │ 0     │ ✗ Out of Stock │
│ Keyboard │ $75   │ 8     │ ✓ In Stock     │
╰──────────┴───────┴───────┴─────────────────╯

=== Example 3: Column Alignment ===
╔═════════════════════╦════════════════╦══════════════════╦══════════╗
║ Left                ║     Center     ║            Right ║ Mixed    ║
╠═════════════════════╬════════════════╬══════════════════╬══════════╣
║ Short               ║  Medium Text   ║ A Very Long Text ║ Normal   ║
║ Very Long Text Here ║      Mid       ║            Short ║ Another  ║
║ Text                ║ Another Medium ║              Mid ║ Last Row ║
╚═════════════════════╩════════════════╩══════════════════╩══════════╝

=== Example 4: Performance Test (Byte-first) ===
┌────┬────────┬───────┐
│ ID │ Data   │ Value │
├────┼────────┼───────┤
│ 1  │ Item_1 │ 1.50  │
│ 2  │ Item_2 │ 3.00  │
│ 3  │ Item_3 │ 4.50  │
│ 4  │ Item_4 │ 6.00  │
│ 5  │ Item_5 │ 7.50  │
└────┴────────┴───────┘

=== Example 5: Unicode Support ===
╭──────────┬─────────────────┬──────╮
│ Language │ Greeting        │ Flag │
├──────────┼─────────────────┼──────┤
│ English  │ Hello World     │ 🇺🇸   │
│ Japanese │ こんにちは世界  │ 🗾   │
│ Chinese  │ 你好世界        │ 🇨🇳   │
│ Korean   │ 안녕하세요 세계 │ 🇰🇷   │
│ Arabic   │ مرحبا بالعالم   │ 🇸🇦   │
╰──────────┴─────────────────┴──────╯

=== Example 6: Table as String ===
Table stored in variable:
+---------+-------+
| Item    | Count |
+---------+-------+
| Apples  | 42    |
| Bananas | 17    |
| Oranges | 8     |
+---------+-------+
Table string length: 140 characters

